languages.text: "Мы на рубеже вероятностей, вне пространства прогнозов. Мы не можем знать, получится у нас или нет".
"We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."
languages.original_text: "Мы на рубеже вероятностей, вне пространства прогнозов. Мы не можем знать, получится у нас или нет".

traits.locale_text: "We are at the edge of probabilities, outside the predictable space. We cannot know for sure whether we will be able to do this or not."
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: « Nous sommes au seuil des probabilités, au-delà des limites du prévisible. Il est impossible de savoir si nous y parviendrons ou non. »
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."

traits.locale_text: « Nous sommes au seuil des probabilités, au-delà des limites du prévisible. Il est impossible de savoir si nous y parviendrons ou non. »
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: «Estamos en el umbral de las probabilidades, fuera de los límites de lo predecible. No tenemos forma de saber si lo que estamos intentando es posible».
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."

traits.locale_text: «Estamos en el filo de las probabilidades, fuera del espacio predecible. No podemos saber con certeza si lo que estamos intentando es posible».
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: “我们身处概率的阈值，在可预测的空间之外。我们无法确切得知我们是否能做得到。”
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."

traits.locale_text: “我们身处概率的边缘，在可预测的空间之外。我们无法确切得知我们是否能做得到。”
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: "Wir stehen an der Schwelle von Wahrscheinlichkeiten und jenseits der Grenzen der Vorhersehbarkeit. Es ist unmöglich, zu wissen, ob wir es können oder nicht."
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."

traits.locale_text: "Wir stehen am Rand aller Wahrscheinlichkeiten, außerhalb des vorhersehbaren Raums. Wir können nicht mit Bestimmtheit wissen, ob uns das gelingen wird."
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: 「我々は確率の縁、予測不可能な空間の外にいる。これが成就するのかし得ないのか、それを知ることは不可能だ」
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."

traits.locale_text: 「我々は確率の縁、予測可能な空間の外にいる。これができるかどうかは、まだ全くわからない」
traits.speaker: NomosDemonEngine

languages.text: "Olasılıkların eşiğinde, tahmin edilenin sınırları dışındayız. Başarılı olup olmayacağımızı bilmek imkânsızın ötesinde."
languages.original_text: "We stand at the threshold of probabilities and outside the bounds of the predictable. It is beyond possible to know whether we can or cannot."
